  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project was approved as part of the Bank&apos;s response to the Covid-19  pandemic. To avoid delays to the delivery the Bank&apos;s President granted a  deviation from the ordinary timelines for PSD disclosure as set out in Section  V of the Directive on Access to Information. Details of the Bank&apos;s response to  Covid-19, and this deviation, can be found on our website.  Provision of a senior loan of up to EUR 5 million under the Resilience  Framework in favour of Mikrofin d.o.o. Banja Luka (the &quot;company&quot;), a limited  liability company incorporated in Bosnia and Herzegovina. The loan will be  split in two equal tranches of EUR 2.5m each with Tranche 2 uncommitted.</narrative>
  </description>
